590
00:41:36,780 --> 00:41:39,180
Your painting is astonishing.

591
00:41:40,340 --> 00:41:43,740
It's nothing. It just takes time.

592
00:41:44,660 --> 00:41:45,984
I can paint you

593
00:41:45,984 --> 00:41:47,820
