594
00:41:48,980 --> 00:41:50,020
That's inappropriate.

595
00:41:50,700 --> 00:41:51,980
Only a painting

596
00:41:51,980 --> 00:41:54,620
can capture your beauty
and keep it throughout the years.

597
00:41:56,780 --> 00:41:59,320
You have to sit still for that. It's boring.

598
00:41:59,320 --> 00:42:01,820
I bet you're too busy for that.

599
00:42:02,660 --> 00:42:03,900
Please don't make fun of me.

600
00:42:03,900 --> 00:42:06,300
I'm idling around all day.

601
00:42:08,700 --> 00:42:10,540
